Pre-Game Insights: United Arab Emirates and United States of America will lock horns in the 33rd ODI of ICC CWC League 2 2024 on Tuesday, 24 September 2024, at Wanderers Cricket Ground, Windhoek.
In a thrilling encounter, the United Arab Emirates clinched a narrow victory over Namibia by one wicket in Match 29 of the ICC CWC League 2.
In Match 31 of the ICC CWC League 2, the United States secured a convincing 7-wicket victory over Namibia.
